---
title: Mild North Indian Lentil Bowl with Turmeric-Roasted Cauliflower & Cucumber Raita
description: Look forward to dinner with this wholesome and nutritious bowl of lentils. Along with gently spiced turmeric cauliflower, roasted cashews and a creamy cucumber raita, this is a veggie delight sent from the heavens.
